title: AFIP-8: Arabella/Matic LP
body: We decided to only form the Arabella/USDC liquidity pool when launching the coin. We did this to reduce the use of arbitrage bots, that could negatively affect the price of AL.  Would you like to  to see an Arabella/Matic liquidity pool added to the arabella.farm 'pair' page?
author: 0x8537Cc6499889DEfbe7e3847218cb61392fAE0De
